snippet.title: Quaver - Open Source Rhythm Game Teaser
snippet.description:
Quaver is a community-driven and open-source competitve rhythm game with two game modes and online leaderboards. It also features an in-game editor and a flexible multiplayer mode

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/980610/Quaver/
Website: https://quavergame.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/QuaverGame
GitHub: https://github.com/Quaver
